The other 4,5 ml were spinned down in hte Megafuge for 5 min, 4000 rpm &ndash;Alle the pellets were rather small so the Samples were put into the Shaker under the same conditions for a couple more hours;
The ordered Primer for Restriction Overhang PCR were diluted in TE-Buffer, so that the concentration is 100 µM;

